fields.name: Switcheo TradeHub
fields.tagline: Switcheo TradeHub node binaries
fields.description: Switcheo TradeHub is a purpose-built sidechain for trading. It is run by a decentralized network of public nodes that each hosts a copy of Switcheo’s order matching engine, validating every trade submission. After validation and execution of trades on Switcheo TradeHub, transactions is broadcasted in batches to be settled on Layer-1 blockchains such as Bitcoin, Ethereum and Neo. The order matching engine is based on our existing, proven off-chain order matching engine, which has thus far been running on centralized servers hosted by Switcheo.
